title: A to Z - 72 - Christmas Music Videos - Xvid - Slimoo
description:
72 - A to Z - Christmas Music Video - Xvid - Slimoo

OK what this is

After posting a smaller version I got request for a bigger one
This version is 4 hours 27 minutes long with 72 non-repeted tracks
(Unless 2 singers released they own verion, West)




I recorded about 16 hours of those Christmas Video Shows
You know the type, 40 biggest Xmas hits, 20 biggest Xmas hits

I then chopped them up to remove adverts and the Host

I then took the 72 vids and created this 4 hour 27 minute video

All the classics and some that where there because there was some snow in the video

Elton John, Slade, Wizard, Cliff, Hall And Oats, Wham, The Pogues, S Club 7, Westlife, Bing, Bowie, Queen, McCartney, Greg Lake, Band Aid

I decided to lay on the tracks from A to Z by Artist Name
So starts with ABBA ends with Wizzard
(This will help you locate any track you want to hear)




As this is likely only played for a week or 2 I never put to much effort into the edits
Just simple fades


Seed until Christmas so everyone gets a decent speed
